<CENTER>
<H1>eCACTI: An Enhanced Power Estimation Model
for On-chip Caches</H1>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1><A href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~maheshmn">Mahesh Mamidipaka</A> and <A href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~dutt">Nikil Dutt </A>
<BR><A href="http://www.cecs.uci.edu/"> Center for Embedded Computer Systems (CECS) </A></CENTER>
</font>
<BR>
<HR>

<CENTER>[<A href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~maheshmn/eCACTI/main.htm">Home</A> |
